Robert P. van Brugge 
Executive Compensation
As Chairman and CEO of SCB LLC at ALLIANCEBERNSTEIN L.P., Robert P. van Brugge  made $4,224,696 in total compensation.  Of this total $400,000 was received as a salary, $1,890,000 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $1,610,000 was awarded as stock and $324,696 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


